Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:20.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:26.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're very excited, aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:30.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Because I bought a brand new swimsuit\Nand floating ring just for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:34.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:38.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you run, you'll trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:44.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:51.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's a hole in the floating ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:53.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aw, man. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:55.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's all wrinkly now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:00:59.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A sudden rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:06.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Demons—!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:09.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:13.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My new swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:17.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,First, hide yourself as a high school girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:18.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, as a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:20.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As a human being! Please hide it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:24.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:27.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you some curry, so don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:29.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lady, one curry please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:33.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, we're sold out of curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:37.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh no, she's crying for real...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Binbou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:15.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For you who are far from luxury, Binbou,\Nshall I treat you to foods that are like a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kanemochi is always so sarcastic...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:20.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Crap, but I want to eat, so I'll go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:27.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you put this under your pillow and sleep,\Nyou'll be able to see the feast in your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:46.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My mornings begin with walking Josephine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:58.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The shopping district is very quiet early in the morning,\Nas if everything but me is stopped in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:00.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hello! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:04.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It seems there's an unseasonable typhoon approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:08.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They say it'll be raining hard starting\Nthis evening. I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuji is troubled!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:15.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I like the quiet shopping district in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The shopping district is very quiet early in the morning—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:25.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Very quiet, as if everything except me is—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:26.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:29.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I heard that a typhoon is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:33.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I need to make it so that the vegetables out front\Nwon't fly away in the strong winds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:40.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Um, if these are that heavy,\NI don't think they'll fly away that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:44.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y-yes... well... that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:49.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When I'm walking in the silence of the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:54.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I forget about the hustle and bustle of the day,\Nand it's as if my heart is cleansed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:05:04.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,At the usual ditch, I say a quick hello to the\Nwoman who always comes here to jog...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:12.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I heard there's an unseasonable typhoon coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The typhoons that come during the summer\Nbecome a downpour!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:17.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wonder if my house is okay in terms of leaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know, I have to check my emergency kit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:24.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That has an expiration date!\NMy emergency biscuits are so stale!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:33.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And at the usual vending machine,\NI buy a can of coffee and go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:37.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:51.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What an unexpected place\Nto be affected by the sudden wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to make me feel better, Josephine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To our warm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What is going on from left to right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:20.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hotori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:28.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You went to pick up the paper while brushing your teeth\Nwhen it was blown away by a sudden wind, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:31.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There seems to be an unseasonable typhoon coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Be careful of sudden winds and heavy rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Daddy, take us somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We'll settle for the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Daddy isn't on summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:48.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why don't you have Big Sister\Ntake you to the community pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Awwwwww!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You kids should stop being so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:55.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hotori, please take the dog out for a walk in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:56.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Awwwwww!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:59.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I'm busy today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My kids all turned out to be just like my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:07.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In this house, it seems my only ally is Josephine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Binbou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:13.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Today we were invited by Kanemochi to catch insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:18.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Binbou-kun, put that Japanese beetle\Ninto this gold bug cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh! There are only two bars, so it got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:25.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're cutting costs! It is gold after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:35.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sis, you're going out too? What about the pool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:38.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sis, why are you going to school\Neven if you're on summer vacation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why? Hey, hey, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, why, hey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:43.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, why, hey, hey, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.00,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Why, why, hey, hey?!\N{\rSubtitle}Hey, why, hey, hey, why?!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:49.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm going because I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:58.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You seem to have no worries; I envy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:03.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:15.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Even though I woke up early this morning, I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:23.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh? I thought I was late, but I'm the first one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You are late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:28.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, the only one in summer school is just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gasp, deja vu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:34.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It is no mistake the second time! Why were you late?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:38.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Because my dog seemed so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:41.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I give a poetic excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:46.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Which is not accepted, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:52.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is the final exam, and this is the make-up test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:57.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In the make-up, I gave the same questions,\Nwith only the numbers changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But why did you get a lower score?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:04.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Even if you say that... All I can say\Nis that I was just unlucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:06.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Because I'm writing on intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Intuition?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:11.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just now, you clearly said you wrote on intuition, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:14.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This could overturn the foundations of math.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:16.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A unique concept...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:28.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So that you would be more eager to understand\Non your own, I decided to change it up a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Change?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, Arashiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Detective work and math are similar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:44.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:46.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you try something different,\Nyou may reap results in an unexpected way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm saying this seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You got it? In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:58.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look for the culprit given the limited amount of hints.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:00.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gather information and clues\Nand combine them in an effective manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:04.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And when you've taken away\Nall possible contradictions...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It becomes clear who the culprit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Isn't it just like a mystery novel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:21.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe I went too far... if I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:23.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:24.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:27.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Detective work is math!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:30.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, I feel like I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Inspector Moriaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:46.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Inspector Moriaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, Arashiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did you find out the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:55.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Inspector! This ominous incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...is now a cold case!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, ouch! That hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ouch! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:09.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I used my head today, so I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:13.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Because I was playing with you, I was late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After I finish walking you, I'm gonna take a nap...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:21.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just like summer vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:29.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, not that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't walk on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:40.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't pick up everything! You'll hurt your tummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ahotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:47.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Futabaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:50.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you mean by Futabaka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:52.46,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling Ahotori?!\N{\rSubtitle}Hey, what do you mean by Futabaka?!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:00.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that your dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:04.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:08.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's rude to laugh at someone's pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:09.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I mean... just look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:12.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's a tanuki taking a tanuki for a walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:26.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A t-tanuki is... a tanuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Get her, Josephine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:32.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Bite her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Josephine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Josephine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:39.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't get happy! You're being mocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:50.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hotori, Hotori, wake up, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It seems I'm not a dog, but a tanuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:59.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've decided to go back to the mountains, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:01.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking care of me all this time, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:02.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Josephine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:05.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Take care, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:06.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Josephine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:09.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Josephine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:12.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Jo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:23.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Josephine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:42.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Josephine... went back to the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Josephine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Josephine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:52.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Josephine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.46,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Your home is here!\N{\rSubtitle}The typhoon's here; what's Hotori doing outside?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.67,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Come back!\N{\rSubtitle}The typhoon's here; what's Hotori doing outside?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:13:59.75,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Come back!\N{\rSubtitle}Maybe she's pretending to be in the Takarazuka troupe?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's pretending to be in the Takarazuka troupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:01.00,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Josephine!\N{\rSubtitle}Maybe she's pretending to be in the Takarazuka troupe?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.92,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Josephine!\N{\rSubtitle}She's such a girl.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:03.50,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Josephine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:09.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When I say shake, go like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:13.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you can't even manage "shake,"\Nyou're going to be called a tanuki again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:15.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay. Now, shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:25.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's like I'm trying to lean on a curtain.\NThere's no sign of you being able to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:31.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Living in this house, I have come to realize the ranks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:34.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It probably goes like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:46.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My teacher... when he's teaching math to me,\Nhe must be feeling like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:49.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have to change my ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:56.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It seems the only one who is\Nlower in rank is the tall male...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:58.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Binbou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:04.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, Binbou, I just bought the DVD of a popular movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come and watch it\Non my home theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:07.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's not like—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:09.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's not like I've got anything else to do,\Nplus I haven't seen it, so I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:11.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh! Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just like a popular DVD, isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:17.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you not have a DVD player?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:19.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Binbou-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:25.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hello Binbou. You look like you're having\Nfinancial difficulties as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:26.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:30.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let me invite you to our winter home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:33.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Darn it, every time he talks it rubs me the wrong way,\Nbut if I stay home I'll be cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:34.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:37.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here, it's almost done! You should help us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:58.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That was refreshing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Club activities are almost done, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:10.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lukewarm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:53.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,While I wasn't around you were doing as you please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:13.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:18.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your drink, Your Highness, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:20.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your buns, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,At ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:25.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, a torch, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:27.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A torch, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, a torch, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:33.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys, it's hot! I don't need any torches!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:36.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, I dropped mine, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:37.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fire, poko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:37.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's hot, poko! So careless, poko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:39.21,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey wait a minute!\N{\rSubtitle}It's hot, poko! So careless, poko!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:41.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The hammock is tangled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:46.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's hot! I can't move! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:50.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ugh... Ponpon Fire Mountain... is on fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:51.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:18:00.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For dinner... is sashimi and miso soup okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:03.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh? Weren't you going to make curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:06.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's what I had in mind when I went shopping,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:09.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but this bushy bald guy said,\N"Take some sashimi," and gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:11.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:15.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Take this sashimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:19.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you eat that sashimi,\Nmaybe you'll become immortal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:22.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh... I see. Bushy Bald Guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:24.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sanada's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:29.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Say, I discovered this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:33.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you make a Japanese omelet\Nand add some sugar, it tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:36.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What kind of Japanese omelet\Nhave you been making all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:39.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's the opposite of what you think!\NThe sugar is the secret to the yumminess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:41.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and stuff like mirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:44.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How is that opposite to what I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's put sugar in here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh no you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:50.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's probably very tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:52.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Pretend you were conned into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:54.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sweet is tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:58.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I told you to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:04.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:10.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you don't have anything to do, write some lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lyrics?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:14.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I want to put a song\Nto words that someone else wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:16.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:23.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Since I'm going to the beach with you tomorrow,\NI'll write a verse with "beach" as the theme...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:31.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Seagulls are great..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:35.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Crows, I don't like..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:39.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Bye, Johnny of the port."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:42.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is it bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:43.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Binbou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:55.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hi Binbou, you look like\Nyou're not eating very good food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:58.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've completed the ultimate mixed rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come over and eat some?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:02.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Damn it, it rubs me the wrong way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:04.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But there must be some awesome\Ningredients. I guess I'll go...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:07.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I mixed the koshihikari rice and\Nthe sasanishiki rice at a 6 to 4 ratio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:09.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's no side dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Tatsuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:24.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you waiting on someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:27.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is it the son of the fishmonger?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:33.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hotori is off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:36.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,While there are no unnecessary spectators today...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm going to invite Sanada to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:47.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where's Arashiyama today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:50.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's at the beach. With someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:55.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The beach?! With someone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How can this be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:58.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All because I was dragging my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:01.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Arashiyama and some guy at the beach together...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:06.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If this was the case, I should've taken my\Nchances and confessed my feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:09.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Had she dumped me, I could've gotten over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:12.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But to think I lost just because I was slow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:13.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:16.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gather your courage and invite Sanada!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:16.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Would
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:16.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Would you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:17.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Would you like to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:17.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Would you like to go
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:17.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Would you like to go to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:18.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Would you like to go to the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:18.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Would you like to go to the beach?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:21.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's only eight words and a question mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:27.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,S-say, Sanada... i-if it's all right with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:30.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,W-would... the beach... beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:34.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Would you like, see squid swimming at the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:39.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When it comes to something important\Nlike this, she's so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:41.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, what about the beach?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:43.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What about the beach?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:46.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The beach! I'm going to make it cloudy\Nwith the tears in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:49.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let it rage like my emotions!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:54.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh. Looks like it's starting to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.42,0:21:55.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:59.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My new swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:03.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,First, hide yourself as a high school girl!
